title: Justin Jefferson: I definitely feel like we would have done better with Sam Darnold

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Justin Jefferson: I definitely feel like we would have done better with Sam Darnold
sources.description: “It’s definitely tough. It's tough to watch. I love that he’s in the Super Bowl. I’m happy for him, I want nothing but the best for him," Jefferson said of Darnold.
